'''Ass''' (iɣ ggutn Ussan) nɣ '''Assf''' (iɣ ggutn Usfan) iga-tt tariban 24 n tassaɛin.  Iga ass akud izdin zɣ unqqr n [[tafukt]] ar taɣlya nns. Ass tzggur as tylgi ɣ tifawt ḍfrnt-t-id tinwutci ɣ tdggʷat. Tizwiri nns (s wassaɣ d wammas n yiḍ s wakud adigan) d tiɣzi nna ittkka qqnen s tizi ilkm usggʷas aha qqnen s wadg ahrawan; ɣ ifuyla ikalanen iɣiy wass ad yawḍ ar 6 n iyyirn.

S ussiriw, issumk wass tamrniwt n yiḍ d wass mala myaḍfarn, aynna imsasan d tuttya imdn n wakal i yixf nns s tuqqna s yat tqiffit tawrakalt ittufkan. Tamunt n sa n wussan ar aɣ ttakkan [[imalass]], ttyifkin i sa n wussan ad.

Ɣ umggaru, iqqan d ad nini mas d ass iga t ula wakud illan gr yat tizi d uzkka nns ɣ tizi ad nik d wansa ad nik, s umdya gr tsragt tiss 15 d uzgn n 1 innayr 2968 ar tasragt tiss 15 d uzgn n 2 innayr 2968.

